dc_title_s: Delaware River Harbor Lines: Pennsylvania Shore from mouth of Schuykill River to Greenwich Point, New Jersey Shore from Red Bank to Newton Creek
dc_description_s: Area along Delaware River from Red Bank to Newton Creek in New Jersey to Newton Creek in New Jersey and and Schuylkill River to Greenwich in Pennsylvania. |Map shows parts of League Island, Hopewell Cove, Big Timber Creek, Schuylkill River, Horseshoe Shoal, Newton Creek. Map also has detailed sketches showing locations of stations and a table of courses, bearings, and distances.
